    dc:description "Figures 6 - 11. Cocoons of Rhysipolis taiwanicus Belokobylskij on Rhaphiolepis indica (L.) Lindl. 6 sizes of cocoons 7 - 9 cocoons after hatching 10 - 11 hatched wasps near cocoons." ;
